Package Web/Vue/React projects into desktop/mobile apps in minutes

Guide
🐙

Open Source

PakePlus is open source and you can find its source code on GitHub

💻

Cross Platform

Windows/macOS/Linux/Android/iOS are all supported

🚀

Small Size

The size is smaller than Electron package by about 20 times (less than 5M!)

📲

Mobile Support

Use native framework to package Android and iOS APP, which is smaller and faster

📦

Easy to Use

UI is simple, no need to install any development environment, save time and save money

🧘‍♀️

Simultaneous Compilation

Just minutes, one click to compile multiple platforms, no environment and time anxiety

🌍

Internationalization

Support internationalization, friendly to global users

🎨

Customization

You can customize the application icon, application name, and inject JavaScript code

🍀

Static File Support

Support packaging static html files or Vue/React projects compiled dist

🍔

Local Build

Supports local packaging and does not require environments. only takes 30 seconds

🥥

Without Token

It's okay without Token, local packaging is simple, and no Token is needed

⚔️

Support Apis

Support calling system Apis in JS scripts, such as downloading files, etc

🐞

Debug Support

Support debug mode, whether in preview or release, you can find bugs

🔒

Data Security

PakePlus will not upload any data, all data is stored on your computer

💬

Technical Support

If you encounter any problems during use, you can chat with us
